    },
    {
      "title": "Guided Search 2.0 A revised model of visual search  Psychonomic Bulletin & Review",
      "link": "https://link.springer.com/article/10.3758/BF03200774",
      "snippet": "Abstract An important component of routine visual behavior is the ability to find one item in a visual world filled with other, distracting items. This ability to perform visual search has been the subject of a large body of research in the past 15 years. This paper reviews the visual search literature and presents a model of human search behavior. Built upon the work of Neiss and a subsequent limited-capacity stage that performs other, more complex operations (e.g., face recognition, reading, object identification) over a limited portion of the visual field. The spatial deployment of the limited-capacity process is under attentional control. T in light of new data. The paper is organized into four parts: Part 1 presents the model and the details of its computer simulation. Part 2 reviews the visual search literature on preattentive processing of basic features and shows how the GS2 simulati early vision. In M. Landy & J. A. Movshon (Eds.), Computational models of visual processing (pp",
      "date": "2021-02-05 13:17:12"
    },
    {
      "title": "Visual Studio Emulator报错:Unable to add user to the Hyper-V Administrators group exit code 2220 的解决方法 - 杨炜健的博客 - CSDN博客",
      "link": "https://blog.csdn.net/rerice/article/details/52753835?locationNum=4&fps=1",
      "snippet": "版权声明:本文为博主原创文章,遵循 CC 4.0 BY-SA 版权协议,转载请附上原文出处链接和本声明。 本文链接:https://blog.csdn.net/rerice/article/details/52753835 当你确定启用了Hyper-V,然而运行Visual Studio Emulator里的Android虚拟机时报错,错误提示为:Unable to add user to the Hyper-V Administrators group exit code 2220时,请你注意下你的操作系统。 如果你使用的操作系统是Win10 Home版(家庭版),那么可能确定,你的操作系统是因为没有“本地用户和组”这个系统组件而报错。 我目前的解决方案是重装系统,安装Win10 Pro(专业版),然后再运行Visual Studio Emulator就不会报错,可以正常使用。 我尝试过使用Key直升,但是从家庭版升级到专业版并没有添加“本地用户和组”这个组件,所以还是不能正常运行Visual Studio Emulator,我建议用Win10安装启动U盘或光盘来进行升级,这样才能补全家庭版中缺少的专业版的功能。",
      "date": "2016-10-08 09:25:42"
    },
